  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/PackageDescription\/SupportedPlatform\/DriverKitVersion\ncrawled: 2025-12-14T13:50:06Z\n---\n\n# SupportedPlatform.DriverKitVersion\n\n**Structure**\n\nThe supported DriverKit version.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nstruct DriverKitVersion\n```\n\n## Type Properties\n\n- **v19**: The value that represents DriverKit 19.0.\n- **v20**: The value that represents DriverKit 20.0.\n- **v21**: The value that represents DriverKit 21.0.\n- **v22**: The value that represents DriverKit 22.0.\n- **v23**: The value that represents DriverKit 23.0.\n- **v24**: The value that represents DriverKit 24.0.\n- **v25**: The value that represents DriverKit 25.0.\n\n## Supporting DriverKit\n\n- **driverKit(_:)**: Configures the minimum deployment target version for the DriverKit platform.\n- **driverKit(_:)**: Configures the minimum deployment target version for the DriverKit platform using a custom version string.\n- **driverKit**: The DriverKit platform\n\n## Conforms To\n\n- Sendable\n- SendableMetatype\n\n",
